{"word":"G3724 - ὁρίζω - horízō - hor-id'-zo - Declare","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>horízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hor-id'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Declare"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தீர்மானி, நிர்ணயி, ஏற்படுத்து, நியமி, குறி,வாக்குத்தத்தம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to define, to determine"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3725 - ὅριον - hórion - hor'-ee-on/3725\">G3725</a>; to <i>mark</i> out or <i>bound</i> (&ldquo;horizon&rdquo;), that is, (figuratively) to <i>appoint</i>, <i>decree</i>, <i>specify:</i> - declare, determine, limit, ordain."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3724 - ὁρίζω - horízō - hor-id'-zo/3724\">G3724</a>, <a href=\"#/G4309 - προορίζω - proorízō - pro-or-id'-zo/4309\">G4309</a>, <a href=\"#/G592 - ἀποδιορίζω - apodiorízō - ap-od-ee-or-id'-zo/592\">G592</a>, <a href=\"#/G873 - ἀφορίζω - aphorízō - af-or-id'-zo/873\">G873</a>"}]}